***Waaagh!***

If your Army Faction is Orks, once per battle, at the start of your Command phase, you can call a Waaagh! If you do, until the start of your next Command phase, the Waaagh! is active for your army and:Units from your army with this ability are eligible to declare a charge in a turn in which they Advanced.

Add 1 to the Strength and Attacks characteristics of melee weapons equipped by models from your army with this ability.

Models from your army with this ability have a 5+ Invulnerable Save.


***Detachment***

Get Stuck In: Melee weapons equipped by ORKS models from your army have the [SUSTAINED HITS 1] ability.
